com.mway.bluerange.android.sdk.core.scanning.messages

Class AssetTrackingMessageV1

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mway.bluerange.android.sdk.core.scanning.messages.BeaconMessage
      • com.mway.bluerange.android.sdk.core.scanning.messages.AssetTrackingMessageV1
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class AssetTrackingMessageV1
extends BeaconMessage
    AssetTracking messages are broadcasted by Relution SmartAssets. SmartBeacons will collect these messages to do indoor localization using the RSSI measurements. The message only contains an asset identifier to map the RSSI values to a thing.
